(1302, '40th birthday party', 'My husband, a HUGE fan, is turning 40. I am hosting a surprise party for him at Cherry Hill Lanes (we won\'t be bowling, but there WILL be karaoke). Guests will begin to arrive around 7 o\'clock. I will bring the birthday boy in around 7:30. It would be absolutely incredible to have some of you there for the surprise', '2014-01-25', NULL, 'Clarkston', 'MI', '4846', 0, 1, 1, NULL, NULL),
(1304, 'March of Dimes/ March for Babies', '', '2014-04-27', NULL, 'Rochester', 'MI', '', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(1305, 'Great Lakes Comic-Con', 'This will be our second event at Macomb Community\r\n College. The 501st comes to our shows regularly (The\r\n Great Lakes Comic Expo) and was at our MCC show last\r\n February. We run an annual comic book and toy show at\r\n MCC. This year\'s philanthropy is Reading is\r\n Fundamental (http://www.rif.org/), which\r\n> is focused on children\'s literacy.\r\n', '2014-02-28', NULL, 'Warren', 'MI', '48088', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(1306, 'Dylan fundraiser', 'We are having a fundraiser for a 9 year old boy named Dylan Rheker. Dylan was born with a disorder called neurofibromatosis (NF1). ', '2014-03-09', NULL, 'Chesterfield Township', 'MI', '48051', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(1307, 'Kzoo Baby & Family Expo', 'The Kzoo Baby & Family Expo is the largest family event in SW Michigan! For the past seven years, we\'ve offered a FREE day of family fun in Kalamazoo. Our target audience is young families with children up to age 10. We have worked hard to keep admission completely free so our event is accessible to everyone. ', '2014-02-09', NULL, 'Kalamazoo', 'MI', '49007', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(1308, 'GVSU Athletics Kids Free Day', 'Kids Free Day is a FREE event for all and involves various vendors with kid-friendly promotional items, giveaways, food, games, activities, and mascots. The kids loving taking pictures and hanging out with mascots. The event is aimed at providing a free, fun experience for the West Michigan community children during this cold winter. ', '2014-02-08', NULL, 'Allendale', 'MI', '49401', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(1309, 'FX - Family Experience', 'We will be doing a \"Star War\" drama during this month\'s event - We would love to have a couple guests to walk around during our \"preshow\" meeting kids. (we would not want Darth or Sith due to the amount of little kids present) Typical attendance is about 200 kids.\r\n', '2014-02-01', NULL, 'Rockford', 'MI', '', 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL),
(1310, 'Grand Rapids Griffins', 'The Grand Rapids Griffins Youth Foundation was established in 1995 to expand the opportunities for participation in ice skating and related sports and activities, and to encourage academic excellence, community involvement and healthy lifestyles among the youth of West Michigan.\r\n\r\n', '2014-03-08', NULL, 'Grand Rapids', 'MI', '49503', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(1311, 'Luke LeClaire Benefit', ' Please help support this 2nd grade Clio student! Luke and his family will be traveling to the University of Minnesota Amplatz Children\'s Hospital on January 11th to undergo a long process of a bone marrow transplant. Luke will be hospitalized there for 4 to 6 months for the treatment of Adrenoleukodystrophy', '2014-02-15', NULL, 'Clio', 'MI', '48420', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(1312, 'Briggs Public Library - Star Wars Night', 'It is an evening of Star Wars related events -- games, crafts, etc. We would like to have the characters be present, interact with the kids, help out with a game or craft if they are so inclined. This is the first time we\'ve done this sort of program, and we would like it to be special.\r\n\r\n', '2014-03-11', NULL, 'St Johns', 'MI', '', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(1313, 'MDA Muscle Walk at Ford Field', 'It’s that time of  year again, time to get our entertainment set for our March Muscle Walk.  As you know this is our largest family fighting event.  The event will once again be held at Ford Field, downtown Detroit, on March 22, 2014.\r\n\r\n', '2014-03-22', NULL, 'Detroit', 'MI', '', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
(1314, 'Explorer Elementary School Carnival', 'Hello! I\'m throwing Explorer Elementary\'s School Carnival. We\'ve had Darth Vader visit our cub scout troop in the past at Explorer and he was AMAZING. Loved him! If we could please get a few volunteers out this year I know the kids would flip! All event proceeds go back into our Elementary School for new equipment, books, school computers etc. Anything you can do to help would be great and very appreciated. We would LOVE to have Darth back!! Storm Troopers, Chewbacca, anyone that the little kids can easily recognize as a Star Wars character would be so awesome. The characters will have their own classroom for the event.', '2014-03-07', NULL, 'Caledonia', 'MI', '49316', 0, 1, 1, NULL, NULL),
