(1320, 'Free Comic Book Day', 'Free Comic Book Day is an annual event where community members can go to their local brick and mortar comic shop to pick up specially prepared comic book for free. It is intended as a way for comic lovers and non comic lovers a like to come together and celebrate the beautiful world of comic books... and pick up some free ones at the same time!\r\n', '2014-05-03', NULL, 'Grand Rapids', 'MI', '49503', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
