(1978, ' Kalamazoo Wings Star Wars Night', 'It is our annual Star Wars night with the Kalamazoo Wings hockey team. We are celebrating everything Star Wars. Our team is wearing specialty Star Wars themed jerseys that will be auctioned off and all the proceeds will be going to the United Way of Kalamazoo. Portion of all ticket sales for the event will also be donated to the United Way of Kalamazoo.', '2017-02-03', NULL, 'Kalamazoo', 'MI', '', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL),
