(2043, 'Devos children\'s hospital visit', 'I am reaching out to you today for a very special request. I have a 5-year-old patient whose birthday is next Friday and he absolutely LOVES Star Wars. I am wondering if there is the possibility of having you and/or any of your Star Wars team members come surprise him on his birthday next week? Without giving you specific details about this patient due to HIPAA laws, he has been through quite an extensive medical history that has required many hospitalizations in his short lifespan. He is someone that I have come to know very well, and would love to support him on his birthday. If this is something that you believe would work for you or your team, please let me know and we can discuss more of the specific details. ', '2017-03-31', NULL, 'Grand Rapids', 'MI', '', 0, 1, 1, NULL, NULL),
