(2047, 'Children s Home Society Star Wars Movie Night', 'The staff at the children\'s home is hosting a Star Wars night for all of the boys who live at the facility. Our Thrivent Community has sponsored several events for the boys and when this event came up we immediately thought of you. They plan to have activities from 4:00-5:30 and then the boys will have dinner and watch the movie. They can provide a changing room for everyone and specifics as to where to park.\r\nI would be happy to be the contact person to facilitate everything between the 501st and the Children\'s Home. A little more information about the children\'s home; these boys have lived through some pretty difficult situations. Most of them have bounced in and out of foster homes and in and out of their own homes. Anytime we get the chance to give them something positive to do or think about is a huge success. I think an event like this would make their year. Thank you again for your consideration and please don\'t hesitate to ask if you need anymore information.\r\n', '2017-04-03', NULL, 'Redford', 'MI', '', 0, 1, 1, NULL, NULL),
